Home » sports » TENNIS STARS DURING THAI TOURISM PROMOTION ACTIVITIES TENNIS STARS DURING THAI TOURISM PROMOTION ACTIVITIES October 2, 2015 1:00 am 
Nadal and Djokovic at Grand Palace. Tennis celebrities Rafael Nadal and Novak Djokovic made a visit at the Grand Palace on Friday morning. The current and former world No1 players stopped by at the Bangkok’s main attraction to sign well-wishes book for His Majesty the King. Both will later meet PM Prayut h Chan-ocha and visit the Erawan Shrine before playing their exhibition match in the evening. 62 Viewed
